title: Saved by The Bell Season 4
description: Saved By the Bell originated as a Disney Channel series titled Good Morning, Miss Bliss. This show about a teacher, Miss. Bliss and her students in an Indiana Junior High School was very short-lived. The people at NBC noticed that the show had potential and picked it up after changing a few things. They decided to keep the characters of Mr. Belding, Zack Morris, Lisa Turtle and Screech Powers, while adding new members such as Kelly Kapowski, Jessie Spano and AC Slater. The focus of the series shifted gears as it began to focus on high school students, rather than a middle school teacher and her class.
